Recommends: nvidia-cuda-toolkit | mesa-va-drivers | intel-media-va-driver
Description: Squeeze your videos for easy sharing
 Small MP4 is a video compression tool designed to reduce video file sizes
 for easy sharing and uploading. The tool supports both GUI (egui) and CLI
 interfaces with hardware acceleration capabilities.
 .
 Features:
  - Target file size control (1MB to 50MB)
  - Hardware acceleration support (NVIDIA, AMD, Intel)
  - Both GUI and CLI interfaces
  - Batch processing support